 le. What are some of the positive and negative effects and implications o
 f the "always on" capability of the mobile phone? In what ways is this cu
 lture of immediacy and access intruding on personal and professional life
 \, and why are people\, especially youths\, so accepting of it? Is the "a
 lways on" culture a significant part of modern life\, or can we do withou
 t it?
