CLASS:Portal
CREATED:20240113T210649Z
DESCRIPTION:How does the performative nature of online activism on platfor
 ms like Twitter affect the authenticity and effectiveness of contemporary
  social justice movements? In what ways can individuals strike a balance 
 between performative activism and genuine engagement to ensure inclusivit
 y and meaningful impact within online communities\, without centering the
 mselves in the conversation and detracting from the issue?
