CLASS:Portal
CREATED:20240113T210649Z
DESCRIPTION:To what degree do you believe misinformation\, disinformation\
 , or mal-information should be controlled by social media platforms and/o
 r governments? Should efforts only be focused on education and critical t
 hinking\, or also on moderating content that is posted\, if it could harm
  others? Answer the question by talking about at least one of the three t
 ypes of information mentioned above\, as they all differ slightly.
