CLASS:Portal
CREATED:20240113T210649Z
DESCRIPTION:In the era of information sharing with a click of a button\, w
 hy do you think so many people tend to re-post articles they do not actua
 lly read in full? Or rather\, why do they re-post anything without verify
 ing the information? Why does confirmation bias cause people to dismiss h
 ow and where information is produced? What do people hope to gain from pa
 rticipating in the knowledge economy in this way\, and how can it be miti
 gated?
