BEGIN:VEVENT
CLASS:Portal
CREATED:20240113T210649Z
DESCRIPTION:Looking at Madrigal's article\, how would you analyze the noti
 on of "technoanxiety" and its impact on contemporary society? How do you 
 interpret the author's critique of the digital detox movement as a form o
 f "artificial" human creation\, and the perceived need to disconnect from
  modern technology? How effective is the digital detox movement in terms 
 of returning humanity to nature\, and does this improve individual well-b
 eing?
