BEGIN:VEVENT
CLASS:Portal
CREATED:20240113T210649Z
DESCRIPTION:How do you compare Turkle's position with Jurgenson's? Do you 
 agree with Jurgenson that those who feel a loss of connection are becomin
 g too obsessed with the idea of being offline\, to the point of fetishiza
 tion? Is our newfound appreciation of slowness and boredom simply a react
 ion to an oversaturated world of informatic noise\, but one that will not
  last\, once we get used to it?
