 their autobiography\, the self is already a story and the person is alrea
 dy a profile\, long before any decisions are made in terms of what to inc
 lude or omit. Do you agree? Compared to how you (or people you know) used
  to use social media when it was first becoming popular in the early 2010
 s\, how much do you narrate your self-presentation as a story?
