BEGIN:VEVENT
CLASS:Portal
CREATED:20240113T210649Z
DESCRIPTION:The MATH 137 Course Outline Scavenger Hunt is set up as a quiz
  is to let you explore how to take a quiz in the LEARN platform. Completi
 ng this will also help you become familiar with the different components 
 of a course outline.\nThis quiz is not graded\, and you can retake it as 
 many times as you would like. You will need to refer to the MATH 137 Cour
 se Outline (pdf) to complete the quiz. You can also review the Module 2 C
 ourse Outlines section for clues to where specific course information can
  be found in a course outline. \nPlease note that information used for th
 is quiz was taken from one example of a course outline for a first-year m
 athematics course. Different courses may have their course outlines struc
 tured differently.
DTEND;TZID=Etc/UTC:20240501T035959
DTSTAMP:20240113T210649Z
DTSTART;TZID=Etc/UTC:20240501T035959
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:MATH 137 Course Outline Scavenger Hunt
UID:3334cf9e-c613-43c2-a8f7-bee5082cf77e
END:VEVENT
